Package edu.university.ecs.lab.semantics.util.visitor

Class MsVisitor

java.lang.Object
edu.university.ecs.lab.semantics.util.visitor.MsVisitor
public class MsVisitor extends Object
Core logic class using java parser libraries to pick apart respective classes, methods, method calls, fields, etc and adding them to cache

These methods visitClass, visitField, visitMethod, visitMethodCalls form the contents of the respect raw outputfiles msClassList.json, msFieldList.json, etc

This class heavily relies on the use of JavaParser,
